Dr. Jeff, so we'll have to figure out.

00:02:02.480 --> 00:02:03.960
We'll have to.

00:02:03.980 --> 00:02:04.301
There we go.

00:02:04.361 --> 00:02:04.721
There we go.

00:02:04.740 --> 00:02:04.881
Okay.

