02:41:27.119 --> 02:41:27.519
home.

02:41:27.978 --> 02:41:31.120
And God chose someone outside the tribe to

02:41:31.161 --> 02:41:32.101
call them back home.

02:41:32.380 --> 02:41:33.461
And that is this job.

02:41:34.235 --> 02:41:35.615
And we're going to do this job.

02:41:35.695 --> 02:41:36.856
We're dedicated to it.

02:41:38.417 --> 02:41:40.599
And you are the beneficiaries if you

02:41:40.658 --> 02:41:41.760
capitalize upon it.

02:41:42.620 --> 02:41:44.900
And we will ask nothing from you.

02:41:45.402 --> 02:41:48.463
We will encourage you if you decide that

02:41:48.484 --> 02:41:50.225
you want to take advantage of what God

02:41:50.284 --> 02:41:52.286
is offering, that you read,

02:41:52.566 --> 02:41:55.048
that you educate yourself so that you know

02:41:56.068 --> 02:41:58.350
who God is, what he's offering,

02:41:58.389 --> 02:42:00.069
what he's asking in return,

02:42:00.129 --> 02:42:02.490
how he carries out all of these things

02:42:02.531 --> 02:42:03.611
and what his timeline is.

02:42:03.630 --> 02:42:05.691
The more educated you are,

02:42:05.731 --> 02:42:07.513
the more effective you can be.

02:42:08.052 --> 02:42:10.613
And then we will naturally encourage you

02:42:10.674 --> 02:42:12.134
to share what you have come to know.

02:42:12.994 --> 02:42:13.655
It's essential.

02:42:14.854 --> 02:42:16.876
That way more people can benefit.

02:42:16.915 --> 02:42:18.876
And what you're doing is good for you.

02:42:18.915 --> 02:42:20.297
It's not just good for other people.

02:42:21.862 --> 02:42:23.384
If you engage with us now,

02:42:23.543 --> 02:42:25.565
you devote yourself to learning,

02:42:25.604 --> 02:42:27.546
reading these books at yadaya.com,

02:42:28.066 --> 02:42:29.968
and you participate with us,

02:42:30.427 --> 02:42:33.450
making a contribution to God's people and

02:42:33.750 --> 02:42:35.050
to this end result,

02:42:35.671 --> 02:42:39.573
then you will have the great joy of

02:42:39.632 --> 02:42:41.113
spending time with Yahweh,

02:42:41.234 --> 02:42:43.316
knowing that He appreciates what you have

02:42:43.376 --> 02:42:43.595
done.

02:42:44.362 --> 02:42:46.843
that you've pleased the creator God of the

02:42:46.984 --> 02:42:48.864
universe and that the king who is

02:42:48.924 --> 02:42:49.425
returning,

02:42:49.745 --> 02:42:54.087
you've made his eternity richer by

02:42:54.147 --> 02:42:56.088
contributing to his family.

02:42:57.049 --> 02:42:59.490
And the sense of satisfaction that you

02:43:00.210 --> 02:43:02.152
capitalized on an opportunity you did what

02:43:02.191 --> 02:43:03.372
very few people have done.

02:43:04.191 --> 02:43:05.773
And you came to trust God.

02:43:05.814 --> 02:43:06.513
You listened to him.

02:43:07.094 --> 02:43:08.136
You acted accordingly.

02:43:08.556 --> 02:43:10.298
You were the antithesis of Adam.

02:43:10.317 --> 02:43:14.121
You used Dode as your exemplar.

02:43:14.941 --> 02:43:17.625
And the sense of satisfaction is

02:43:17.684 --> 02:43:18.185
overwhelming.

02:43:18.226 --> 02:43:20.086
There's no other better place to be.

02:43:20.166 --> 02:43:23.370
Rich would be such a wonderful example of

02:43:23.390 --> 02:43:23.591
this.

02:43:23.650 --> 02:43:25.172
Leah is another example of this.

02:43:25.211 --> 02:43:26.773
You guys are all examples of this.

02:43:26.793 --> 02:43:27.735
There's no better place to be.

02:43:30.287 --> 02:43:31.587
And you can see it on our faces.

02:43:31.608 --> 02:43:32.648
You can see it in our eyes.

02:43:32.668 --> 02:43:33.808
You can hear it in the tone of

02:43:33.849 --> 02:43:34.370
our voice.

02:43:35.650 --> 02:43:36.971
We know exactly what we're doing,

02:43:37.051 --> 02:43:37.832
why we're doing it,

02:43:39.173 --> 02:43:41.213
and that you are the beneficiaries if you

02:43:41.314 --> 02:43:41.534
act.

02:43:42.614 --> 02:43:44.397
And you will receive exactly the same

02:43:45.637 --> 02:43:48.699
awards and benefits and inheritance that

02:43:49.079 --> 02:43:49.860
we all have.

02:43:52.141 --> 02:43:53.923
Our future is assured.

02:43:54.824 --> 02:43:56.204
We don't need to do this for us.

02:43:56.305 --> 02:43:59.086
We're doing it for you.

02:43:59.127 --> 02:43:59.666
Capitalize.

02:44:01.414 --> 02:44:01.634
Well,

02:44:01.773 --> 02:44:04.056
now we've gone to two hours and forty-five

02:44:04.095 --> 02:44:06.816
minutes on our family hour on this program

02:44:06.877 --> 02:44:08.018
on Return to the Garden.

02:44:11.039 --> 02:44:11.840
You talk a lot, sir.

02:44:12.479 --> 02:44:15.481
No, you can't be the voice of Yawa,

02:44:15.842 --> 02:44:17.282
the coal of Yawa in this job,

02:44:17.323 --> 02:44:21.145
unless you voice what Yawa wants.

02:44:21.165 --> 02:44:21.465
That's true.

02:44:21.986 --> 02:44:23.686
To make a long story long.

02:44:25.667 --> 02:44:27.007
They said I would have written a short

02:44:27.048 --> 02:44:28.308
letter, but I didn't have the time.

02:44:30.646 --> 02:44:30.786
No,

02:44:31.147 --> 02:44:32.747
we're excited about what we're sharing

02:44:32.768 --> 02:44:33.029
with you.

02:44:33.068 --> 02:44:37.853
We want you to soak it in,

02:44:37.953 --> 02:44:40.397
learn it, share it, benefit from it.

02:44:41.718 --> 02:44:44.322
It's this marvelous story that God has

02:44:44.621 --> 02:44:45.163
offered us,

02:44:45.563 --> 02:44:47.204
and we want you to capitalize upon it

02:44:47.385 --> 02:44:47.966
and celebrate it.

02:44:48.735 --> 02:44:49.775
So thank you, everyone.

02:44:54.097 --> 02:44:55.679
And thanks, Joe.

02:44:55.738 --> 02:44:56.859
Thank you, Joe,

02:44:56.879 --> 02:44:58.340
for getting our books together.

02:44:58.399 --> 02:44:59.120
Thank you, Leah,

02:44:59.140 --> 02:45:01.402
for all of this wonderful branding that

02:45:01.662 --> 02:45:02.242
you're doing.

02:45:02.441 --> 02:45:03.503
Thank you, Dr. Jeff,

02:45:03.522 --> 02:45:06.183
for representing Yisrael so well.

02:45:06.244 --> 02:45:06.543
Kevin,

02:45:06.564 --> 02:45:10.066
you are hugely valuable and it is a

02:45:10.126 --> 02:45:12.487
huge contribution to everything that we're

02:45:12.528 --> 02:45:12.768
doing.

02:45:13.487 --> 02:45:14.189
Captain Kirk,

02:45:14.529 --> 02:45:18.993
you were my brother from another mother,

02:45:19.112 --> 02:45:21.435
and we have been best buds forever and

02:45:21.476 --> 02:45:22.916
will be best buds forever,

02:45:22.957 --> 02:45:26.040
and I've always appreciated your intellect

02:45:26.260 --> 02:45:28.301
and contribution, JB.

02:45:29.382 --> 02:45:31.203
Thank you all so much for being part

02:45:31.245 --> 02:45:32.646
of this show and for my good friend

02:45:32.966 --> 02:45:35.668
Rich there managing behind the scenes.

02:45:36.769 --> 02:45:37.649
Thank you, Rich.

02:45:37.750 --> 02:45:38.329
We're grateful.

02:45:38.409 --> 02:45:39.591
Say Shabbat Shalom, honey.

02:45:39.630 --> 02:45:40.911
Shabbat Shalom to everyone.

02:45:40.932 --> 02:45:42.952
Good night.

02:45:42.972 --> 02:45:43.733
Say good night, dear.

